text: @maddow As of 6 p.m. Friday, there have been 10,268 positive cases of coronavirus (COVID-19) in Florida. The case count includes 9,925 Florida residents and 343 non-Florida residents. There are 170 deaths reported and 1,334 hospitalizations, according to the Florida Department of Health.
